column2: select top # p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.deVRad_r, p.u, p.r, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_u, s.z as RedShift, s.zConf from galaxy as p, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq (#, #, #) as n, galSpecInfo as s where p.objid = n.objid and p.specObjID = s.specObjID and p.specObjID< ># and s.z> # and clean = # order by s.z
